            <thetext>Maybe one could pipe all colors the table use to some kind of appearance entry 
e.g.

&quot;table-colors&quot; :
{
  style : function(states)
  {
    return {
      &quot;row-background-odd&quot; : &quot;background-odd&quot;,
      &quot;row-background-even&quot; : undefined,
      &quot;row-background-selected&quot; : &quot;background-selected&quot;,
    }
  }
}

Just an idea. Not sure how we could do it, but it may be possible that this 
will solve both issues: It makes it possible to still change table colors 
individually, but for the areas where these colors are identical to already 
existing ones these may be used.</thetext>
